metadata.name: Dreamer
metadata.description:
The spirit of youth, freedom and protest.

Malika is a talented young girl, singer, journalist, adventurer and an ardent opponent of the current government in Russia.
We were supposed to have shooting in Moscow a long time ago, but fate turned out that we met by chance in Armenia, where each of us was running away from terrifying reality and the regime.

Erevan, 
May 2022
